<title>HOW GREAT THOU ART !</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Aw Lal Pathien, ka ngaihtuoh tieng mak ka sa'i,
 Na khutsuok leh Na thilsiem haw cheng hi;
 Aksi ka mu'n, van gi lopitak ka zai,
 Na thilhih theihna'n mun tin a zel suok.

[V2]
 Ka thagau in Nang pakna la a sa'i,
 Na lopi ie! Na lopi ie;
 Ka thagau in Nang pakna la a sa'i,
 Na lopi ie! Na lopi ie!

[V3]
 2. Gammangpi thingnuoi a ka vakviel lai in,
 Vacha'n thing a la hawih a sak ka zai;
 Muol sang lopihaw chu ka etviel tieng leh,
 Luicha luonggi, huihchim nun git ka za'i.

[V4]
 3. Pathien in A Cha neihsun chuh hawilo a,
 Thi dinga A hun sawl chuh mak ka sai;
 Kross achun ka gikpuok cheng chuh A pawtai,
 Thisan luong in ka gitloh a la mang.

[V5]
 4. Thawm lopi tawh Krista A hung kit tieng leh,
 Van a ei puih tieng ka lung kipak ding;
 Kingainiem in Amah ho in khun ing ting,
 &quot;Lalpa, Na lopi na e!&quot; ti'n gen ka.</lyrics>
</song>